<class module="baja" runtimeProfile="rt" qualifiedName="javax.baja.tag.util.SmartRelationSet" name="SmartRelationSet" packageName="javax.baja.tag.util" public="true">
<description>
A SmartRelationSet is an implementation of the Relations interface. It maintains separate subsets&#xa; of relations for smart relations and direct relations.  Any methods that would modify the&#xa; relation set only operate on the direct relations.
</description>
